 currently there is no difference since serial-test is skipped in nightly profile and all tests are executed in regular execution (which executes them serially for nightly profile). However maybe in the future we can split nightly profile also to run in two part (regular and serial) - then it can be useful.", "author": "olukas", "createdAt": "2020-02-27T08:25:36Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM4NDk0Mzg3NA=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}]}